  tool tool_coreference
    name coreference
    note "Resolve follow-up pronouns against previous conversation turns before answering."
    mode thinking
    inputs prompt|history
    outputs resolved_subject|answer|evidence
    isolation conversation-history
    sources data/seed/coreference.lino
    localized ru
      name coreference
      note "Разрешает местоимения в последующих вопросах по предыдущим репликам перед ответом."
    localized zh
      name coreference
      note 在回答前根据先前对话轮次解析后续问题中的代词指代。
    localized hi
      name coreference
      note "answer देने से पहले previous conversation turns से follow-up pronouns resolve करता है।"
  tool tool_roleplay
    name roleplay
    note "Respond from grounded persona templates while preserving deterministic symbolic behavior."
    mode thinking
    inputs persona|topic|prompt
    outputs persona_answer|evidence
    isolation seed
    sources data/seed/personas.lino
    localized ru
      name roleplay
      note "Отвечает по grounded persona-шаблонам, сохраняя детерминированное символьное поведение."
    localized zh
      name roleplay
      note 根据有依据的人设模板回复，同时保持确定性的符号行为。
    localized hi
      name roleplay
      note "deterministic symbolic behavior रखते हुए grounded persona templates से जवाब देता है।"
